OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunshine
OL,6,Fand showers on Sunday. Continuing into
OL,7,FMonday with heavy rain, possible
OL,8,Fthunderstorms. Staying unsettled
OL,9,Fthrough the week as temperatures
OL,10,Freturn to average.
